    <item>
      <title>非洲最大杂货商将家具部门出售给竞争对手 Pepkor</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/africa-s-largest-grocer-sells-furniture-unit-to-rival-pepkor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大的连锁超市 Shoprite Holdings Ltd. 将把其家具部门出售给一家规模较小的竞争对手，因为这家非洲最大的连锁超市专注于扩大其在本土市场的食品业务，以及发展专业服装、婴儿、户外和宠物商店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/africa-s-largest-grocer-sells-furniture-unit-to-rival-pepkor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:23:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在丰厚的绿色拍卖中加大对海上风电的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/uk-boosts-support-for-offshore-wind-in-bumper-renewables-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在去年拍卖失败后，英国政府试图重振海上风电行业，将支持建设 4.9 千兆瓦的新海上风电场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/uk-boosts-support-for-offshore-wind-in-bumper-renewables-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
